### Admin Module API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v1
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@userId = YOUR_USER_ID_HERE

### ==============================================
### DASHBOARD & OVERVIEW
### ==============================================

### 1. Get Comprehensive Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. Get Dashboard Statistics (30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard?period=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. Get Dashboard Statistics (7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard?period=7d
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4. Get Activity Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/trends?days=30
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==============================================
### USER MANAGEMENT
### ==============================================

### 5. List All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6. Search Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?search=demo&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Filter Users by Role
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?role=USER&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Filter Active Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?isActive=true&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9. Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10. Update User
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": true,
  "role": "USER"
}

### ==============================================
### DOCUMENT MANAGEMENT
### ==============================================

### 11. List All Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/documents?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 12. Filter Documents by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/documents?status=SIGNED&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13. Filter Documents by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/documents?userId={{userId}}&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14. Search Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/documents?search=test&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==============================================
### SIGNATURE MANAGEMENT
### ==============================================

### 15. List All Signatures
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/signatures?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 16. Filter Reusable Signatures
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/signatures?isReusable=true&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 17. Filter Signatures by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/signatures?userId={{userId}}&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==============================================
### STATISTICS
### ==============================================

### 18. Get User Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 19. Get Document Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 20. Get Signature Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats/signatures
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==============================================
### SYSTEM MONITORING
### ==============================================

### 21. Get System Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/health
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 22. Get System Health (Detailed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/health?detailed=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 23. Get System Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==============================================
### CACHE MANAGEMENT
### ==============================================

### 24. Clear Admin Cache
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/cache
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==============================================
### CURL Examples
### ==============================================

# Get Overview
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/overview" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# List Users
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/users?page=1&limit=20" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Get Dashboard Stats
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/dashboard?period=30d" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Get System Health
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/health?detailed=true" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"

# Update User
# curl -X PATCH "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/users/USER_ID" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"isActive": false}'

# Clear Cache
# curl -X DELETE "http://localhost:5001/api/v1/admin/cache" \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"
